      "name": "Centrifugal VAD hemolysis applicability domain",
      "description": "Model is applicable to centrifugal blood pumps operating within the FDA generic pump geometry envelope, with blood viscosity in the range 3.0–4.5 mPa·s, hematocrit 35–45%, and rotational speeds 2000–3500 RPM. Extrapolation beyond these bounds is not supported by the validation evidence base."
