      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry — the same geometry class as the COU device. Operating conditions in validation span the COU envelope. Blood analog fluid (glycerol-water) used; departure from whole blood is documented as a known input uncertainty captured in Monte Carlo UQ.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
