      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on published benchmark performance for confined rotating flows. Power-law hemolysis damage accumulation model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) used per FDA guidance. Model form uncertainty estimated at ±12% on NIH via comparison with alternative turbulence model (RNG k-epsilon, ±8% deviation).",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
