        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "Simulation boundary conditions must be traceable to measured experimental conditions. Deviations in inlet flow rate must be below 5% and outlet pressure below 3 mmHg. Fluid property equivalency must be documented in a traceability matrix."
